Hi Rafaella,
Thanks for the response. We will consider and determine outcomes for all th=
e points you have raised below. This does occur normally as a part of our n=
ormal work process =E2=80=93 but I am acknowledging your request to have th=
ese processes documented in specific detail =E2=80=93 so this will take me =
some time to respond to each enquiry individually.
The asbestos survey is the first process gateway, and this is the correct o=
rder in which to move through each item you have highlighted.
To that end the licensed Asbestos Surveyor who will attend to complete the =
survey is Warren Webber from =E2=80=98Green Check=E2=80=99, WORKSAFE licens=
e number AA19050008.
The weblink to Greencheck is below for your reference:
Greencheck New Zealand | Environmental Compliance Experts [greencheck.co.nz=
]<https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/greencheck.co.nz/__;!!NPvfczxIteVBjg!B=
Mh_pn6K08iTATIvDbaPeNx5P9jgoJtNjFLpWcTQOZRrxNtTCDbUT0SAJAAvhuBiuMa-gUHXAV2V=
g6n2ErFbC7H8RQ$>

Please reply when you can with your confirmation to undertake this process =
on July 9 as prescribed.
Regards,
Grant.


[cid:image001.png@01DBF00D.0EFCA100]
Grant Metson
Regional Manager - House Assessing
Phone 021 744 288
Level 5, 136 Fanshawe Street,
PO Box 90347, Auckland 1142

