e a live document that will gather detail
 as we progress.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ca=
libri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">However, I do trust=
 that this will give you some insight and knowledge to allow us to particip=
ate in the process together.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-fam=
ily:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I look forward to s=
peaking with you soon.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&q=
uot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please confirm back=
 via email when you get a chance that you agree for Asset Restore to undert=
ake the asbestos survey on the 9<sup>th</sup><span class=3D"xapple-converte=
d-space">&nbsp;</span>=E2=80=93 as this is the first
 step in the process.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&qu=
ot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
